	(OCO)-O-16-C-13-O-18, (OCO)-O-16-C-13-O-17, (CO2)-C-12-O-18, (OCO)-O-17-C-12-O-18,
	(CO2)-C-12-O-17, (CO2)-C-13-O-18, (CO2)-C-13-O-17, (OCO)-O-17-C-13-O-18,
	and (CO2)-C-14-O-16 isotopologues, the differences are between +/-
	0.10 and 0.15 cm(-1). To our knowledge, this is the first time a
	polyatomic PES has been refined using such high J values, and this
	has led to new challenges in the refinement procedure. An initial
	high quality, purely ab initio dipole moment surface (DMS) is constructed
